2537,IssuesEvent,2017-10-07 01:23:00+00:00,4742675,jbittel/django-mama-cas,1647454,diegoduncan21,,,opened,about single logout,[],[],0,"I'm using MAMA_CAS and MAMA_CAS_NG, I want to log out from all services when I log out from the primary server.
