2742,IssuesEvent,2018-03-23 20:22:05+00:00,106754007,WhyNotHugo/python-barcode,17056237,henniss,,,opened,Comment doesn't display package version,[],[],0,"When I write a Code128 barcode in Python3, I get the following:

