4631,IssuesEvent,2017-06-23 11:31:01+00:00,41740681,inveniosoftware/invenio-access,1698163,lnielsen,1157480,inveniosoftware,closed,caching: arguments are not taken into account leading to wrong permissions,"[{'id': 414883324, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio-access/labels/Size:%20hard', 'name': 'Size: hard', 'color': 'a828a8', 'default': False}, {'id': 255123790, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio-access/labels/Type:%20bug', 'name': 'Type: bug', 'color': 'ff2a00', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'diegodelemos', 'id': 9035606, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/9035606?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/diegodelemos', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/diegodelemos/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",1,"The [caching layer](https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio-access/blob/master/invenio_access/permissions.py#L93-L95) does not take the action argument into account.

E..g if the action is ``edit`` with argument ``1`` , and the caching layer will just get any previous cached result for the ``edit`` action, which could be e.g. ``edit`` with argument ``2``. This is essentially leads to wrong permissions being applied when caching is used.",{},{}
4632,IssuesEvent,2017-06-11 09:38:43+00:00,41740681,inveniosoftware/invenio-access,1698163,lnielsen,1157480,inveniosoftware,opened,caching: arguments are not taken into account leading to wrong permissions,"[{'id': 255123790, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/inveniosoftware/invenio-access/labels/Type:%20bug', 'name': 'Type: bug', 'color': 'ff2a00', 'default': False}]",[],0,"The [caching layer](https://github.com/inveniosoftware/invenio-access/blob/master/invenio_access/permissions.py#L93-L95) does not take the action argument into account.

E..g if the action is ``edit`` with argument ``1`` , and the caching layer will just get any previous cached result for the ``edit`` action, which could be e.g. ``edit`` with argument ``2``. This is essentially leads to wrong permissions being applied when caching is used.",{},{}
