_""error"": ""Internal server error: Unable to compute variable 'revenus_capitaux_prelevement_bareme' for period 2018: 'revenus_capitaux_prelevement_bareme' must be computed for a whole month. You can use the ADD option to sum 'revenus_capitaux_prelevement_bareme' over the requested period, or change the requested period to 'period.first_month'.""_
