5752,IssuesEvent,2016-03-30 21:30:41+00:00,7209075,pantsbuild/pants,596358,wisechengyi,3065172,pantsbuild,closed,Remove GraphValidator,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/pantsbuild/pants/labels/engine', 'name': 'engine', 'color': 'fbca04'}]",[],3,"The `scheduler.GraphValidator` addresses a usecase that is very specific to the prototype implementation of targets under `src/python/pants/engine/exp/examples/`: namely, the case where only one literal config value has been provided in a BUILD file. It's also super, super slow for repeated runs because it re-validates the entire graph, rather than just the portion that changed.

