    Routing mesh...
    deis-router@2.service: loaded
    deis-router@3.service: loaded
    deis-router@1.service: loaded
    Done.
    
    Please run `deisctl start platform` to boot up Deis.

So I did not run deisctl start platform, because I want to restore previous data. According to http://docs.deis.io/en/latest/managing_deis/backing_up_data/ I executed

    $ deisctl start store-monitor

I took forever so I finally CTRL-C'd it and logged into the server and checked: `journalctl -u deis-store-monitor`

    Aug 18 20:23:50 cloud-1 systemd[1]: Starting deis-store-monitor...
    Aug 18 20:27:50 cloud-1 systemd[1]: deis-store-monitor.service stop-sigterm timed out. Killing.
    Aug 18 20:27:50 cloud-1 systemd[1]: deis-store-monitor.service: control process exited, code=killed status=9
