    Aug 18 20:27:50 cloud-1 systemd[1]: deis-store-monitor.service failed.

Strange. I wanted to check on the overall system. So I executed `systemctl list-units`
The usual system services are running, update-engine.service is `masked` as it should be, but:

    user-cloudinit@var-lib-coreos\x2dinstall-user_data.path                  loaded active     running         Watch for a cloud-config at /var/lib/coreos-install/user_data
