See that `docker.service`? It's inactive. Dead. I guess it should be running. See what causes the troubles, shall we? `journalctl -u docker.service`

    -- Logs begin at Tue 2015-08-18 20:19:03 UTC, end at Tue 2015-08-18 20:57:11 UTC. --
