```
In simple lightweight app this operation just spawn many process with one instance and one version. With hardcore big java app (big image) it makes registry slow down and make starting application 1 - 3 hours. Also no one can deploy or start any new containers due this configuring will be resolved.

We really need to create lock on any operations in controller with containers.",{},{}
