Then, i upload the fat jar to a linux system with this configuration: 
```
spark-shell --jars xxx-assembly-1.0.jar,BigDL/dist/lib/bigdl-0.2.0-SNAPSHOT-jar-with-dependencies.jar --properties-file BigDL/dist/conf/spark-bigdl.conf --driver-memory 20G --executor-memory 20G --num-executors 16


