`java.lang.NoSuchMethodError: com.intel.analytics.bigdl.nn.SpatialConvolution$.apply$mFc$sp(IIIIIIIIIZLcom/intel/analytics/bigdl/nn/InitializationMethod;Lscala/reflect/ClassTag;Lcom/intel/analytics/bigdl/tensor/TensorNumericMath$TensorNumeric;)Lcom/intel/analytics/bigdl/nn/SpatialConvolution;
