8678,IssuesEvent,2017-07-19 19:35:53+00:00,56847043,nfcpy/nfcpy,6625545,falkartis,18479744,nfcpy,opened,Use with SPI bus,[],[],0,"I'm trying to use a PN532 board over the SPI bus on a raspberry pi.

I've followed this tutorial https://www.itead.cc/blog/raspberry-pi-drives-itead-pn532-nfc-module-with-libnfc And managed to get the ID from a mifare tag, but I didn't find a way to read it's content.
